item.title: 波音发现737MAX新隐患[0-50]
item.description:
波音发现737MAX新隐患 Boeing warns about possible wing problems on some 737 Max planes
The Federal Aviation Administration released a statement Sunday saying Boeing has informed them that some parts for the company's grounded 737 Max passenger plane, and prior model 737 Next Generation, may have been improperly manufactured. CBSN New York has the details.
CNBC报道波音称737MAX的机翼也可能存在问题。
